                {
                    "$checked": true,
                    "$disabled": false,
                    "$visible": true,
                    "description": "The Wwise Audio Lab is a game-like 3D environment showcasing various spatial audio phenomena using different methods and tools such as comparing static with dynamic early reflections, experimenting with sound portals, oriented reverb, occlusion and obstruction, audio LOD (level of detail), ambisonics vs. quad, binaural vs. standard stereo, etc. In this package you get the compiled game running on Windows, Mac, Oculus and Vive and the full Wwise project.",
